# Project Overview

**Project name:** University Recommend

University Recommend is a full-stack web application that helps high school students find suitable universities and majors based on:

- student score and subject combination
- preferred major and career interests
- preferred location and university type
- tuition budget
- admission methods and historical cutoff scores

A **local Ollama chatbot** (target) explains results in natural language. Factual data always comes from **PostgreSQL**, not from the LLM alone.

## Main users

- Student
- Parent
- Admin
- Career advisor / teacher

## Main features

### Student (target)

- register and login
- create student profile
- search universities and majors
- view university / major detail and cutoff tables
- submit preferences and receive recommendations
- save favorites (planned)
- use chatbot for guidance

### Admin (target)

- manage universities, majors, university–major links, cutoff scores, admission methods
- manage users
- review chat data if needed

